# CLAUDE.md — Project Memory (Template)

> This is a reference template showing the Anthropic-recommended CLAUDE.md
> convention (April 2026). Target: under 80 lines, scannable in one screen.
> `/setup-AI-Pulse-Georgia` writes a stack-specific version of this at
> project root on first run. The global/user layer at `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md`
> adds your personal rules on top; this file captures project-specific facts.

